data.description: Nestled in a serene cul-de-sac, just a leisurely stroll away from the highly coveted Walton High School, this meticulously maintained residence boasts a refreshing ambiance of home. Freshly painted throughout and basking in natural light, step inside to discover the allure of hardwood floors guiding you through the inviting living spaces. A focal point of comfort awaits in the cozy family room, where the masonry fireplace invites evenings of warmth and relaxation. The heart of the home, a delightful eat-in kitchen, exudes charm and functionality and is adorned with new stainless steel appliances, including a refrigerator and gas stove. Revel in culinary adventures while enjoying meals in this delightful space. The recently tiled and updated powder room offers a touch of modern luxury for guests and residents alike. The staircase, just recently redone with a rustic charm, leads to three generously sized bedrooms, designed with a split bedroom floor plan for further privacy. The master suite reigns supreme and features a dual vanity ensuite. Whether you're entertaining guests or simply enjoying everyday moments, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Situated in the extremely sought-after Walton school district and surrounded by homes approaching million-dollar prices ... this home reflects both a solid investment for future wealth and a wonderful place to raise your family. Don't miss the opportunity to make this haven your own and experience the epitome of suburban living, where every day feels like a retreat.
